text: 1. I can’t get enough of the trader joe’s aglio olio seasoning. I could probably go through one jar every two weeks. 2. These look like the most perfect migas. Making them! 3. It’s summer reading list week! Oh my gosh, maybe my favorite week of the year? Coming soon! 4. Sometimes I put this on a post it: buying stuff won’t make you happy! 5. TV things!! Your Friends and Neighbors is getting crazy! 6. Open calendar space is life-changing for me. 7. Jordan’s birthday is coming up and he keeps saying he wants a “head cake.” A cake with his face on it. Well okay! 8. Who to thank for diet coke. Hello, yes.
html:
1. I can’t get enough of the trader joe’s aglio olio seasoning. I could probably go through one jar every two weeks.

2. These look like the most perfect migas. Making them!

3. It’s summer reading list week! Oh my gosh, maybe my favorite week of the year? Coming soon!

4. Sometimes I put this on a post it: buying stuff won’t make you happy!

5. TV things!! Your Friends and Neighbors is getting crazy!

6. Open calendar space is life-changing for me.

7. Jordan’s birthday is coming up and he keeps saying he wants a “head cake.” A cake with his face on it. Well okay!

8. Who to thank for diet coke. Hello, yes.
